root: ^That's LORD Smellingham to you, filthy commoner! Actually, it's "Lord Whinnies Phlerbius Smellingham, Fourth of His Name, Order of the Albionese Empire." But "Lord Smellingham" will do.
^Ok... so, what can I do for you, Lord Smellingham?
^I have come to collect this week's rent. Per the existing arrangement, that will be £<THREE-QUARTERS OF REVENUE EARNED>
